├── 7105. 報表分析功能群_SRS.md          # S-401~S-406 (Phase 5,6)
│   ├── Phase 5: S-401, S-402, S-403
│   └── Phase 6: S-404, S-405, S-406
└── 7106. 系統設定功能群_SRS.md          # S-501~S-507 (Phase 6,7)
    ├── Phase 6: S-501, S-502, S-503
    └── Phase 7: S-504, S-505, S-506, S-507



    
